4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer." This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and aims to kickstart their career as a data scientist. The course duration is 16 weeks, with 3 classes per week. It covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, and focuses on creating predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy. Students will also learn about supervised and unsupervised learning models, and have the opportunity to work on real-life cases. The course is available in English and Spanish, and classes are taught in the language of the student's campus. The course is led by experienced instructors, including Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop